# Keycloak token flow cho mini-lab
# Điều kiện:
# - Keycloak đang chạy tại http://localhost:18080.
# - Realm `viettel-lab` đã được tạo.
# - Client `tenant-demo-api-client` đã bật Direct access grants.
# - User `tenant1-user`, `tenant2-user` đã có password và attribute tenant_id.
#
# Không commit access token thật vào file này.

@keycloakUrl = http://localhost:18080
@realm = viettel-lab
@clientId = tenant-demo-api-client
@tenant1User = tenant1-user
@tenant2User = tenant2-user
@password = password

### OpenID Provider metadata
GET {{keycloakUrl}}/realms/{{realm}}/.well-known/openid-configuration

### JWKS endpoint
# Lấy jwks_uri từ request metadata ở trên nếu path khác.
GET {{keycloakUrl}}/realms/{{realm}}/protocol/openid-connect/certs

### Token tenant 1 bằng password grant - local lab only
POST {{keycloakUrl}}/realms/{{realm}}/protocol/openid-connect/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=password&client_id={{clientId}}&username={{tenant1User}}&password={{password}}

### Token tenant 2 bằng password grant - local lab only
POST {{keycloakUrl}}/realms/{{realm}}/protocol/openid-connect/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=password&client_id={{clientId}}&username={{tenant2User}}&password={{password}}

